beer.beer_description:
I Am Froot is our latest Brewpub Series Release- A bold American style IPA coming in at 6.9% ABV. Available in keg only 

Packed full of grapefruit and lime with an aggressive bitterness and slightly tart finish. American hops and lupulin powder contribute to the punchy aromatics of citrus and dank pine needle that hang around longer than Vin Diesel’s acting career. 

This brew is outta this world and super limited.
